EN: Ignoring safety standards is not conducive to safeguarding lives.

ZH: 不珍惜时间不利于提高工作效率。
EN: Not cherishing time is not conducive to improving work efficiency.

ZH: 不合理的消费习惯会不利于理财。
EN: Unreasonable spending habits are detrimental to financial management.

